column2: select sl.stable_id as case_list_id, max(sl.name) as case_list_name ,      max(sl.description) as case_list_description ,      sl.cancer_study_id ,      STRING_AGG(s.stable_id ,&&&) as case_ids   from cancer_study cs     inner join sample_list sl       on sl.CANCER_STUDY_ID=cs.CANCER_STUDY_ID   join sample_list_list sll      on sl.list_id=sll.list_id   join sample s     on s.internal_id=sll.sample_id where cs.cancer_study_identifier=&&& group by sl.stable_id,sl.cancer_study_id order by #,#
